cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.MM 

The paper deals with interference estimation and avoidance in cellular networks, which is a topic closely related to network infrastructure (NI). The paper also involves mathematical modeling and analysis of power spectrum measurements, which falls under information theory (IT) and mathematical analysis (MA). The paper proposes a technique for interference avoidance, which can be seen as a control system (SY) problem. Finally, the paper applies the proposed technique to an opportunistic transmission technique, which involves multimedia (MM) communication.
